/*
   Class: Polar

   A multi purpose polar representation.

   Description:
 
   The <Polar> class, just like the <Complex> class, is used by the <Hypertree>, <ST> and <RGraph> as a 2D point representation.
 
   See also:
 
   <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polar_coordinates>
 
   Parameters:

      theta - An angle.
      rho - The norm.
*/

